(1628, 193, 'service_section_service_blanks_3_service_blank_image', '132'),
(1629, 193, 'service_section_service_blanks_4_service_blank_title', 'Consulting on your questions'),
(1630, 193, 'service_section_service_blanks_4_service_blank_desc', ' Consulting on issues related to foreign economic activity, currency regulation, customs legislation of the Republic of Belarus and the Customs Union. <br><br>\r\nTimely answers to pressing questions, as well as professional assistance in the preparation and execution of documentation, will allow you to avoid many problems and make foreign economic activity as profitable as possible.'),
(1631, 193, 'service_section_service_blanks_4_service_blank_image', '133'),
(1632, 193, 'service_section_service_blanks_5_service_blank_title', ' Analysis of foreign trade transactions'),
(1633, 193, 'service_section_service_blanks_5_service_blank_desc', 'Outsourcing of foreign trade activities – provision of a range of services for import and export\r\ngoods for the client. <br><br>\r\nBy entrusting us with the support of foreign economic activity, you save yourself from many difficulties associated with the import and export of goods. We will undertake to fulfill all formalities in the field of international trade.'),
(1634, 193, 'service_section_service_blanks_5_service_blank_image', '134'),
(1635, 193, 'service_section_service_blanks_6_service_blank_title', 'A range of services for sorting, reloading, labeling, transshipment and storage of goods'),
(1636, 193, 'service_section_service_blanks_6_service_blank_desc', 'We have our own warehouse, on the territory of which we use modern access control systems and\r\nvideo surveillance. The warehouse provides a full range of services for sorting, reloading, labeling, transshipment, and storage of goods.'),
(1637, 193, 'service_section_service_blanks_6_service_blank_image', '135'),
(1638, 193, 'service_section_service_content_0_content', 'Our company is a warehouse holder and provides <b>services for sorting, reloading, labeling, transshipment, storage of goods and other customs operations</b> with goods transported by road and rail vehicles and under customs supervision.'),
(1639, 193, 'service_section_service_content_1_content', 'Extensive experience and professionalism, a high level of competence and education of our company’s employees allows us to <b>quickly prepare the appropriate package of documents and reduce the time required for customs clearance, guaranteeing its quality</b>, which in turn allows us to carry out customs clearance of cargo “on the same day”. day\".'),
